"Zahlungsmethoden` und klicken Sie auf :guilabel:`Neu`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:103
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Journal` field to :guilabel:`Cash`."
msgstr "Setzen Sie das Feld :guilabel:`Journal` auf :guilabel:`Bargeld`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:104
