msgid "QFPay configuration"
msgstr "QFPay-Konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:18
msgid "To configure a QFPay payment terminal, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Um ein QFPay-Zahlungsterminal zu konfigurieren, führen Sie die folgenden "
"Schritte aus:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:20
msgid ""
"Create a QFPay account on the `QFPay website <https://qfpay.global/products/"
"qfpay-pos-api/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Erstellen Sie ein QFPay-Konto auf der `QFPay-Website <https://qfpay.global/"
"products/qfpay-pos-api/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:21
msgid ""
"Request the activation of `Asynchronous Notifications <https://sdk.qfapi.com/"
"docs/common-api/asynchronous-notification/>`_ from QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Beantragen Sie die Aktivierung von `asynchronen Benachrichtigungen <https://"
"sdk.qfapi.com/docs/common-api/asynchronous-notification/>`_ bei QFPay."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:23
msgid ""
"Provide the Odoo server address to QFPay, followed by `/qfpay/notify`, and "
"copy the notification key provided by QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie die Odoo-Serveradresse an QFPay weiter, gefolgt von `/qfpay/"
"notify`, und kopieren Sie den von QFPay bereitgestellten "
"Benachrichtigungsschlüssel."

