msgid ""
"Enter **9001** (if using an :doc:`IoT box </applications/general/iot/"
"iot_box>`) or **9050** (if using a :doc:`Windows virtual IoT </applications/"
"general/iot/windows_iot>`) on the **Network domain name** screen and press "
"**OK** twice."
msgstr ""
