msgid "Check the :guilabel:`Urban Piper` setting."
msgstr "Kreuzen Sie die Einstellung :guilabel:`Urban Piper` an."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:173
msgid "Set up UrbanPiper:"
msgstr "Richten Sie UrbanPiper ein:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:175
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Api Key` fields with "
"your :ref:`UrbanPiper credentials <pos/urban_piper/credentials>`."
msgstr ""
"Füllen Sie die Felder :guilabel:`Benutzername` und :guilabel:`API-Schlüssel` "
"mit Ihren :ref:`UrbanPiper-Zugangsdaten <pos/urban_piper/credentials>` aus."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:177
msgid ""
"Select the desired delivery providers in the :guilabel:`Food Delivery "
"Platforms` field under the :guilabel:`Urban Piper Location` section (i.e., "
"Zomato, Uber Eats)."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie den gewünschten Versanddienstleister im "
