#~ "Um diese Produktbeziehungen zu importieren, **müssen** *zunächst* die "
#~ "Datensätze der verknüpften Objekte aus deren eigenem Listenmenü "
#~ "importiert werden."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "On product forms in Odoo, there are a number of fields that can be "
#~ "modified and customized at any time. These fields are found under every "
#~ "tab on a product form. While these fields are easily editable directly on "
